 role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sup1665702611757.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sup1665702611757.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sup1665702611757.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sup1665702611757\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Vertical Scaling (\n                              Vscale)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Image</span> data types. Default value is <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">100</code> (percent).\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sup1665702611757__p_d99818e1_d99819e1_d99820e1\">\n         \n                                Vscale\n                                <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Percentage</var> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Auto</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sup1665702611757__table_d11600e1_d11601e1_d11602e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sup1665702611757__table_d11600e1_d11601e1_d11602e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sup1665702611757__table_d11600e1_d11601e1_d11602e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sup1665702611757__table_d11600e1_d11601e1_d11602e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Percentage</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sup1665702611757__table_d11600e1_d11601e1_d11602e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Positive integer from <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">10000</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sup1665702611757__table_d11600e1_d11601e1_d11602e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Auto</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sup1665702611757__table_d11600e1_d11601e1_d11602e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Scale the image to fit the width of the widget. Instead of preserving the aspect ratio, it stretches the image to fit the widget.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sup1665702611757__section_z5k_w2l_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d635376e146\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sup1665702611757__table_d11603e1_d11604e1_d11605e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported in Grid?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes for Picture</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sup1665702611757__section_e4t_x2l_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d635376e210\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sup1665702611757__p_d99827e1_d99828e1_d99829e1\">If the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Preserve Aspect</span> property\n            is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, the larger of <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Horizontal Scale</span> and\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Vertical Scale</span> properties are ignored.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sup1665702611757__section_ufl_z2l_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d635376e231\">Command Button</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sup1665702611757__p_d99833e1_d99834e1_d99835e1\">For command buttons, this property only works if the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Representation</span> property is set to\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sup1665702611757__section_ak5_bfl_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d635376e247\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"sup1665702611757__pre_nzl_dfl_swb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(PICTURE)=\"vscale=auto\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sup1665702611757__section_gt4_dfl_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d635376e256\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"sup1665702611757__ul_ebv_2fl_swb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sup1665702611757__li_d40340e1_d40341e1_d40342e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ujj1665702610581.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ujj1665702610581.html\" title=\"Area frames are objects that can be used to group or separate the contents of a Form component.\">Area Frames and Lines</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sup1665702611757__li_d40343e1_d40344e1_d40345e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iic1718342502908.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iic1718342502908.html\" title=\"The udefentity widget is the default widget for entities in form components. It is a multi-occurrence list, with a minimum of one occurrence, in which fields can be freely arranged. Uniface provides a default logical widget called DefEntity that is mapped to this widget.\">udefentity (Default Entity Widget )</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sup1665702611757__li_d40346e1_d40347e1_d40348e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxc1665703126500.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxc1665703126500.html\" title=\"The upicture widget is used to displays the contents of an Image field. Uniface provides a logical widget called Picture, which is mapped to upicture.\">upicture (Picture)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"sup1665702611757__ul_mbv_2fl_swb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sup1665702611757__li_d40352e1_d40353e1_d40354e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ula1665702613468.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ula1665702613468.html\" title=\"An Entity defines a logical data aggregation. It usually represents a relational database table, but it is possible to define non-database entities for transient data, reusable user interface controls, or other application structures.\">Entities</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sup1665702611757__li_d40355e1_d40356e1_d40357e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scc1665702611448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702611448.html\" title=\"Image used as background for the application window, form, or entity. This property can be set in ProcScript.\">Background Image (BackImage)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbd1665702611680.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale)</a><p>This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/btj1665702631955.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Representation</a><p>This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a><p>Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent). Vscale = Percentage | Auto Value Description Percentage Positive integer from 1 through 10000 . Auto Scale the image to fit the width of the widget. Instead of preserving the aspect ratio, it stretches the image to fit the widget. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? Yes for Picture Dependencies: None Description If the Preserve Aspect property is True , the larger of Horizontal Scale and Vertical Scale properties are ignored. Command Button For command buttons, this property only works if the Representation property is set to Uniface . Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(PICTURE)=\"vscale=auto\" Copy Applies To Area Frames and Lines udefentity (Default Entity Widget ) CommandButton upicture (Picture) Entities Background Image (BackImage) Related Links Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale) This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent). Representation This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header. Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}